> _Qustion:_
> 
> What will cause (more?) speed up of the game:
> 
> - If I will start this game on PPC on 750 mhz and Permedia2 or
> - If I will start this game on PPC on 166 mhz AND RivaTNT gfx card?

Both will have an impact. On  fast machines with 200+ MHz, or 604 CPU,
the graphics card slows down  the operation.  It could theoreticaly go
much faster with a decemt (i.e. non-Permedia2) card.

On slower machines (603e with less  than 180 MHz) both the CPU and the
graphics  card are  limiting the  frame rate.  There is  some  kind of
break-even point  where the graphics card is  really nearly saturated,
but the CPU cannot deliver more data. A faster card would not help. 

